videos.description: Kevin Harris powers his way to the end zone to get South Carolina on the board first for the two-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Harris scores the contested TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris scores the contested TD

videos.description: Dameon Pierce rushes in the easy two-yard touchdown as the Gators respond quickly in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pierce walks in untouched as Florida responds) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pierce walks in untouched as Florida responds

videos.description: Kyle Trask rolls out and throws the perfect pass to Kyle Pitts for the Gators touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Trask connects with Pitts for the 13-yard TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trask connects with Pitts for the 13-yard TD

videos.description: Shi Smith takes a quick hit as he enters the end zone leading to the tying score against the Gators.

videos.headline: Smith bounces off a defender to score South Carolina TD
